note.p:
Pub. L. 99–145, title V, § 504(c), Nov. 8, 1985, 99 Stat. 622, as amended by Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 809(c)(2), Aug. 13, 2018, 132 Stat. 1841, provided that: “Section 9414(b)(2) of title 10, United States Code (as added by subsection (a)(1)(B)), and section 5102(c)(28) of title 5, United States Code (as added by subsection (b)), shall not apply to any person who on the date of the enactment of this Act [Nov. 8, 1985]— “(1) is a civilian member of the faculty of the United States Air Force Institute of Technology;
“(2) is paid a rate of basic pay under the General Schedule; and
“(3) elects, under procedures prescribed by the Secretary of the Air Force, to continue to be paid under the General Schedule.”
